1. *Gužva* na ulici je bila nepodnošljiva. (The *crowd* on the street was unbearable.)
2. Moramo stići na vreme, a u ovom *gužvanju* će nam biti teško. (We need to arrive on time, and it will be difficult in this *traffic*.)
3. Sinoć je bila ogromna *gužva* u klubu. (There was a huge *crowd* in the club last night.)
4. *Gužva* u redu za kupovinu bila je prevelika. (The *crowd* in the shopping line was too big.)
5. Vozači moraju biti pažljivi kada se kreću kroz *gužvu* na putu. (Drivers must be careful when navigating *traffic* on the road.)
6. Uvijek imamo *gužvu* u restoranu vikendom. (We always have a *crowd* at the restaurant on weekends.)
7. Moramo pronaći neki način da izbegnemo *gužvu* na aerodromu. (We need to find a way to avoid the *crowd* at the airport.)
8. Ova *gužva* na stanici će nam otežati ukrcavanje na voz. (This *crowd* at the station will make it difficult for us to board the train.)
9. U gradskom prevozu uvek postoji *gužva* u jutarnjim časovima. (There is always *crowding* in public transportation during the morning hours.)
10. Moramo biti strpljivi u ovoj *gužvi* i ne gubiti živce. (We need to be patient in this *crowd* and not lose our nerves.)